Decouple and Scale Applications using Amazon SQS and Amazon SNS

Payload and Attributes
	- Key/Value pairs
	- With business meaning:
		- CustomerID=6445
		- MessageType=NewBooking

	- With technical meaning:
		- SourceHost=ip-
		- ProgramName=WebServer-PID:0889

SQS Standard Queue
FIFO Queue

Amazon SNS
 Publisher > SNS Topic > Subscriber (Lambda/SQS/HTTP)

 Message Streams
 	 - ordered 
 	 - also known as shards and partitions

 